div.span:
Entry Point
src/server/index.js
Purpose: Server initialization
and lifecycle management
Pattern: Factory/Initialization
Responsibilities:
• Load config
• Configure logger
• Initialize Server
• Graceful shutdown

Server
src/server/server.js
Purpose: WebSocket server
and message orchestration
Pattern: Facade
Responsibilities:
• WebSocket lifecycle
• Connection handling
• Message routing
• State broadcasting
• Client-to-player mapping

ConnectionManager
src/server/ConnectionManager.js
Purpose: Connection lifecycle
and metadata management
Pattern: Registry/Manager
Data Structures:
• connections: Map
• playerIdMap: Map
Responsibilities:
• Track connections
• Map clientId to playerId
• Store metadata

GameServer
src/server/GameServer.js
Purpose: Game state management
and player operations
Pattern: Domain Model
Data Structures:
• players: Map
Responsibilities:
• Player lifecycle
• Move validation
• State serialization
• Collision detection

Game
src/game/Game.js
Purpose: Core game state
container
Pattern: Aggregate Root
State:
• score: number
• running: boolean
Responsibilities:
• Board initialization
• Score tracking
• Game running state

Board
src/game/Board.js
Purpose: Game board grid
representation
Pattern: Value Object
Data Structure:
• grid: 2D array
- '#' walls
- '.' empty
Responsibilities:
• Grid initialization
• Cell access
• Wall checking
• Serialization

MessageHandler
src/network/MessageHandler.js
Purpose: Message parsing
and creation utilities
Pattern: Utility/Helper
Functions:
• parseMessage()
• createMessage()
Responsibilities:
• Parse JSON
• Validate structure
• Add timestamps

MessageTypes
src/network/MessageTypes.js
Purpose: Message type
constants
Pattern: Constants/Enum
Types:
• CONNECT
• MOVE
• STATE_UPDATE
